            <c id="ref10" level="series">
                <did>
                    <unittitle>Series I: New York City September 11 Memorials</unittitle>
                </did>
                <scopecontent id="ref29">
                    <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                    <p>Series I contains eighteen images from the photographer's series of the same name. The photographs are all black and white, 11x14 prints, and show memorials for people who died during the World Trade Center collapse. Many show public and private memorials to firefighters. Others show more public memorials, such as a fence where memorial tiles were hung. All the photographs were taken in 2002.</p>
                    <p>Prints are arranged chronologically by month.</p>
                </scopecontent>
